No wonder the MCAs have turned their positions into cash cows so that every time the chips are down, they bring up all sorts of accusations to blackmail governors so that their selfish demands can be met.
This issue needs to be addressed clearly in future legislations so that errant MCAs are shown the door as fast as the governors are being impeached.
